'''Cory''' is a documentary filmmaker who tried to make a film about a "haunted" house.

==History==
Cory, Hattie, and Tobias were making a documentary about the Hackett Murder House when Tobias and Cory ended up trapped in the house while Hattie escaped. Hattie called for help and station 19 responded. Maya, Travis, Theo, and Sullivan entered the house to search for them while Hattie remained outside. Maya and Sullivan searched the downstairs while Travis and Theo checked upstairs. Maya and Sullivan found Tobias, who was trapped under a fallen shelf. They freed him and took him out. Then they noticed Travis and Theo weren't reachable by radio. Tobias informed them there was a trap door in the house, so they went back in and searched for it. When they found it, they broke through it and evacuated Travis, Theo, and Cory, who had all fallen down there.

==Relationships==
===Professional===
He works with [[Tobias]] and [[Hattie]], making documentary films.

==Career==
He makes documentary films.
